						<div class="postbody">You can only put games that use the same mapper and games that use trivial mappers (e.g. NROM) in the same cart. You'll want to somehow add a second mapper that controls the upper address lines while the cart's own mapper controls the lower address lines.
<br />
<br />And have you considered developing your own NES software too?</div>

